gh%20her%20portfolio%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20meeting%2C%20Portillo%20expressed%20her%20trepidation%20to%20her%20agents%20at%20Trump%20Model%20Management%20%E2%80%94%20the%20modeling%20agency%20founded%20in%201999%20by%20now-former-President%20Donald%20Trump%20%E2%80%94%20and%20told%20them%20that%20Richardson%20had%20worn%20only%20a%20robe%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20waved%20away%20her%20distress%2C%20her%20suit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrump%20Model%20Management%20dismissed%20her%20concerns%2C%20telling%20her%20that%20such%20behavior%20was%20commonplace%20and%20that%20given%20Mr.%20Richardson's%20prominence%20and%20influence%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20Ms.%20Portillo%20should%20overlook%20his%20behavior%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agents%20booked%20a%20photoshoot%20with%20Richardson%20for%20that%20May%2C%20according%20to%20the%20suit.%20When%20she%20arrived%20at%20his%20studio%2C%20an%20employee%20offered%20a%20beverage%20that%20made%20her%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20dizzy%2C%20disoriented%2C%20and%20not%20fully%20in%20control%20of%20her%20body%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20photoshoot%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%2C%20Richardson%20instructed%20her%20to%20remove%20her%20clothing%20before%20forcing%20her%20to%20perform%20oral%20sex%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20tried%20to%20push%20Mr.%20Richardson%20away%20and%20attempted%20to%20back%20away%20from%20him.%20But%20she%20was%20closely%20surrounded%20by%20Mr.%20Richardson's%20employees%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20were%20cheering%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges.%20%26quot%3BMr.%20Richardson%20had%20his%20hand%20on%20her%20head%2C%20keeping%20her%20in%20place.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%20and%20his%20employees%20snapped%20photos%20while%20he%20sexually%20abused%20her%2C%20Portillo's%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%20had%20another%20appointment%20with%20Richardson%20the%20next%20day%2C%20for%20a%20fashion%20brand%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20She%20%26quot%3Battempted%20to%20tell%20an%20agent%20at%20Trump%20Model%20Management%20about%20the%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20lawsuit%20says%2C%20but%20the%20agency%20%26quot%3Binsisted%20that%20she%20proceed%20with%20the%20appointment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%2C%20Richardson%2C%20and%20other%20members%20of%20the%20photography%20crew%20traveled%20in%20a%20van%20back%20to%20Manhattan%20from%20the%20shoot%20location.%20In%20the%20van%2C%20Richardson%20%26quot%3Bunbuckled%20his%20pants%2C%20grabbed%20her%20head%2C%20and%20forced%20it%20towards%20his%20penis%20without%20her%20consent%26quot%3B%20before%20commanding%20her%20to%20perform%20oral%20sex%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20alleges%2C%20also%20while%20his%20staff%20took%20photos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%20returned%20to%20Spain%20a%20week%20later%2C%20abandoning%20her%20modeling%20career%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERichardson%20included%20the%20photos%20in%20a%20book%20and%20gallery%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%20has%20faced%20numerous%20sexual%20assault%20accusations%20since%20the%20early%202000s%20and%20was%20effectively%20ousted%20from%20the%20fashion%20industry%20in%202017%20amid%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement.%20An%20attorney%20for%20Richardson%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20Portillo's%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%20had%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.es%2Fmoda%2Fnews%2Farticulos%2Fminerva-portillo-terry-richardson-modelo-historia-acoso-sexual-verdad%2F31964%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecounted%20her%20story%20in%202017%2C%20to%20Vogue%20Spain%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20brought%20her%20new%20lawsuit%20in%20Manhattan%20federal%20court%20under%20the%20Adult%20Survivors%20Act%2C%20a%20New%20York%20law%20passed%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20%23MeToo%20movement%20that%20created%20a%20one-year%20window%20permitting%20accusers%20to%20bring%20civil%20sexual%20misconduct%20lawsuits%20that%20would%20otherwise%20be%20barred%20by%20the%20statute%20of%20limitations.%20The%20window%20for%20new%20lawsuits%20closes%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223056%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Minerva%20Portillo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e6a5c22cf74a5739bcb3f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222292%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMinerva%20Portillo%20at%20a%20Vogue%20Spain%20event.%3Cp%3EGabriel%20Maseda%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20Richardson%2C%20corporate%20entities%20related%20to%20Trump%20Model%20Management%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffashion%2Fshortcuts%2F2017%2Fapr%2F11%2Ftrump-model-agency-closing-mother-jones%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhich%20stopped%20operating%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20named%20as%20defendants%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%20Attorneys%20representing%20those%20entities%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20does%20not%20identify%20the%20particular%20agents%20who%20represented%20Portillo%20and%20booked%20the%20meetings%20with%20Richardson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20to%20Ms.%20Portillo%20was%20foreseeable%20and%20preventable%2C%20because%20she%20had%20shared%20her%20concerns%20about%20working%20with%20Mr.%20Richardson%20with%20Trump%20Model%20Management%2C%26quot%3B%20Aleix%20Cuadrado%2C%20a%20Spain-based%20attorney%20representing%20Portillo%20in%20the%20case%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichardson%20published%20the%20photos%20allegedly%20depicting%20Richardson's%20sexual%20assault%20in%20a%20photo%20gallery%20and%20a%20book%2C%20and%20sold%20at%20least%20one%20of%20them%20to%20a%20private%20collector%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20The%20photos%20depict%20Portillo%20gripping%20Richardson's%20penis%2C%20Portillo%20performing%20oral%20sex%20on%20him%2C%20and%20Richardson%20ejaculating%20on%20Portillo's%20face%20while%20she%20wears%20his%20glasses.%20Richardson%20often%20photographed%20models%20wearing%20his%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo's%20lawsuit%20says%20she%20signed%20a%20release%20form%20for%20the%20photos%2C%20but%20that%20she%20did%20not%20understand%20what%20the%20form%20said%20because%20her%20native%20language%20is%20not%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20form%20falsely%20states%20the%20photos%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20depict%20actual%20sexually%20explicit%20conduct%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortillo%20relied%20on%20her%20agents%20at%20Trump's%20management%20company%20to%20handle%20release%20forms%20for%20her%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20provocative%20%E2%80%94%20but%20consensually%20made%20%E2%80%94%20art%2C%20and%20sexual%20assault%2C%26quot%3B%20Christine%20Dunn%2C%20another%20one%20of%20Portillo's%20attorneys%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BMs.%20Portillo%20alleges%20that%20this%20was%20the%20latter%2C%20and%20Mr.%20Richardson%20did%20not%20have%20the%20rights%20to%20distribute%20the%20images.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-model-agency-dismissed-concern-terry-richardson-sex-abuse-lawsuit-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700687320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655e6a219c7d23cb3b9f0982%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-model-agency-dismissed-concern-terry-richardson-sex-abuse-lawsuit-2023-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20model%20met%20with%20Terry%20Richardson%2C%20who%20was%20wearing%20only%20a%20robe%2C%20she%20expressed%20concern.%20Her%20agents%20working%20for%20Trump%20brushed%20it%20off.%22%2C%22