ses%2F1008279%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20American%20Association%20for%20the%20Advancement%20of%20Science.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20putting%20his%20penis%20inside%20the%20vagina%2C%20the%20male%20bat%20just%20sticks%20his%20part%20near%20the%20female's%20opening%20and%20holds%20it%20there%20until%20the%20job%20is%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20behavior%20is%20well%20known%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Finternational%2Fnews%2Fscientists-discover-how-dinosaurs-peed-pooped-and-had-sex-using-an-all-purpose-orifice%2Farticleshow%2F80421770.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eit's%20the%20first%20time%20ever%20that%20it's%20been%20observed%20in%20a%20mammal%2C%20the%20researchers%20said%20in%20their%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20peer-reviewed%20journal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcell.com%2Fcurrent-biology%2Ffulltext%2FS0960-9822(23)01304-0%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECurrent%20Biology%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%2C%20you%20might%20ask%2C%20did%20scientists%20get%20here%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBats%20with%20shockingly%20giant%20penises%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20when%20the%20scientists%20put%20the%20bats%20under%20anesthesia%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20their%20reproductive%20biology%2C%20they%20noticed%20that%20the%20males%20were%20incredibly%20well-endowed%2C%20Nicolas%20Fasel%2C%20lead%20author%20of%20the%20paper%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Lausanne%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFasel%20explained%20that%20the%20sheer%20size%20and%20shape%20of%20the%20organ%20were%20shocking%20to%20them.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20just%20had%20to%20anesthetize%20the%20bats%2C%20we%20could%20see%20their%20erection.%20And%20then%20we%20were%20just%20like%2C%20'Wow.%20What%20is%20that%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20erect%2C%20the%20bats'%20penises%20were%20on%20average%200.65%20inches%20long