%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22225055%2FF_VzHUgWAAAFMcQ.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffour-indian-army-officers-including-2-captains-killed-in-encounter-in-jks-rajouri%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20militant%20was%20reportedly%20also%20killed%20in%20the%20encounter%20which%20is%20still%20ongoing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffour-indian-army-officers-including-2-captains-killed-in-encounter-in-jks-rajouri%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Will%20AI%20Become%20Sentient%3F%20What%20'Father%20Of%20Internet'%20Told%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%20should%20not%20be%20conflated%20with%20real%20human%20intelligence%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20depended%20on%20for%20crucial%20things%20like%20%26quot%3Bretirement%20finance%20planning%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmedical%20diagnosis%26quot%3B%2C%20Dr%20Vint%20Cerf%2C%20the%20father%20of%20Internet%2C%20has%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%20The%20reason%20is%20that%20such%20systems%20currently%20are%20far%20from%20perfect%2C%20indicated%20Dr%20Cerf%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20the%20Chief%20Internet%20Evangelist%20of%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArtificial%20intelligence%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20a%20manifestation%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20general%20form%20of%20machine%20learning%26quot%3B%20and%20it%20can%20reflect%20only%20what%20it%20has%20learnt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20an%20example%20of%20what%20could%20be%20a%20real-life%20situation%2C%20he%20said%20a%20voice-activated%20AI%20could%20do%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20you%20do%20not%20want%20it%20to%20do%26quot%3B.%20For%20example%2C%20it%20could%20open%20the%20door%20to%20a%20visitor%20but%20without%20checking%20who%20the%20visitor%20is%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Blarge%20language%20models%20possibly%20doing%20you%20do%20not%20want%20it%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20bunch%20of%20edge%20cases%20and%20nuances%20that%20programmers%20should%20look%20into.%20These%20are%20the%20kind%20of%20things%20that%20worry%20me%20and%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20we%20are%20getting%20to%20a%20point%20where%20AI%20systems%20can%20become%20self-aware%2C%20Dr%20Cerf%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20the%20answer%20is%20no%26quot%3B.%20Programmers%2C%20he%20said%2C%20need%20more%20time%20to%20understand%20the%20peculiarities%20of%20these%20systems.%20Giving%20an%20example%2C%20he%20said%20the%20larger%20AI%20models%20are%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bhallucinating%20models%26quot%3B%20since%20they%20%26quot%3Bconflate%20factual%20information%20and%20produce%20counter-factual%20output%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20effect%20of%20deepfakes%20in%20the%20coming%20days%2C%20he%20said%20it%20could%20create%20concern%20in%20the%20entertainment%20industry.%20Deep%20fakes%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20hazard%26quot%3B%20so%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20regulated%20and%20a%20mechanism%20should%20be%20prepared%20to%20make%20people%20creating%20them%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700673120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fagcbjslo_vint-serf_625x300_22_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-exclusive-correct-to-be-concerned-about-ai-potential-vint-cerf-father-of-internet-tells-ndtv-4597778%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Artificial%20intelligence%20should%20not%20be%20conflated%20with%20real%20human%20intelligence%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20depended%20on%20for%20crucial%20things%20like%20%26quot%3Bretirement%20finance%20planning%26quot%3B%20and%20medical%20prescriptions%26quot%3B%