ent%2Fhindi%2Fweb-stories%2Ffrom-rocky-to-gangubai-when-directors-praised-actors-for-portraying-complex-characters%2Fphotostory%2F105423530.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jewellery%20Firm%20Runs%20Rs%20100-Crore%20'Ponzi%20Scheme'%2C%20Agency%20Conducts%20Searches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Trichy-based%20jewellery%20chain%2C%20which%20has%20branches%20in%20several%20places%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry%2C%20including%20Chennai%2C%20is%20under%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20radar%20for%20running%20an%20alleged%20Ponzi%20scheme%20and%20duping%20investors%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%20The%20agency%20has%20conducted%20searches%20on%20the%20properties%20of%20some%20people%20associated%20with%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20stores%20run%20by%20the%20firm%20had%20suddenly%20shut%20in%20October%20and%2C%20based%20on%20complaints%2C%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20in%20Trichy%20had%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20owner%2C%20who%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Madhan.%20Lookout%20notices%20had%20also%20been%20issued%20against%20the%20owner%20and%20his%20wife%20earlier%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20issued%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20ED%20said%20it%20was%20investigating%20the%20case%20registered%20by%20the%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20and%20had%20conducted%20searches%20on%20Monday%2C%20under%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%202002%2C%20against%20some%20of%20the%20people%20accused%20of%20running%20the%20Ponzi%20scheme.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20said%20Rs%2023.7%20lakh%20in%20cash%2C%20bullion%20and%20gold%20jewellery%20weighing%2011.6%20kg%2C%20and%20some%20incriminating%20documents%20have%20been%20seized%20during%20the%20searches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%20Rs%20100%20crore%20had%20been%20collected%20by%20Pranav%20Jewellers%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20gold%20investment%20scheme%20which%20promised%20high%20returns.%20Not%20only%20did%20the%20returns%20not%20materialise%2C%20but%20the%20amount%20invested%20had%20also%20not%20been%20given%20back%20to%20the%20investors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20firm%20and%20the%20accused%20cheated%20the%20public%20by%20diverting%20funds%20to%20shell%20entities%20and%20accommodation%20entry%20providers%20under%20the%20garb%20of%20purchasing%20bullion%20or%20gold%20ornaments.%20Accommodation%20entry%20providers%20help%20companies%20commit%20fraud%20or%20evade%20taxes%20by%20bringing%20unaccounted%20income%20back%20into%20the%20books%20and%20making%20them%20look%20like%20legitimate%20transactions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20said%20the%20searches%20revealed%20that%20some%20suppliers%20in%20the%20books%20of%20Pranav%20Jewellers%20were%20entry%20providers%20and%2C%20during%20the%20investigation%2C%20they%20had%20confessed%20to%20having%20provided%20accommodation%20entries%20to%20the%20firm%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore.%20They%20had%20also%20confessed%20to%20giving%20cash%20to%20the%20accused%20in%20return%20for%20bank%20payments%2C%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700670300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fuvocqub_ed-generic-enforcement-directorate-generic_625x300_20_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjewellery-firm-runs-rs-100-crore-ponzi-scheme-agency-conducts-searches-4597548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Trichy-based%20jewellery%20chain%2C%20which%20has%20branches%20in%20several%20places%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Puducherry%2C%20including%20Chennai%2C%20is%20under%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20radar%20for%20running%20an%20alleged%20Ponzi%20scheme%20and%20duping%20investors%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22en