ndiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmeet-the-influential-women-behind-argentinas-president-elect-javier-milei%2Farticleshow%2F105422733.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmeet-the-influential-women-behind-argentinas-president-elect-javier-milei%2Famp_articleshow%2F105422733.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fmeet-the-influential-women-behind-argentinas-president-elect-javier-milei%2Famp_articleshow%2F105422733.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMurder%2C%20Murder%2C%20Murder%26quot%3B%3A%20When%20IAF%20Gnat%20Jets%20Shot%203%20Pak%20Sabres%20In%201971%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%20in%20East%20Pakistan%20reached%20a%20climax%20with%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20wars%20fought%20in%20modern%20history%20which%20led%20to%20splitting%20Pakistan%20into%20two%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistani%20army's%20genocide%20in%20East%20Pakistan%20created%20a%20problem%20of%20refugee%20influx%20for%20India%20and%20Since%201947%2C%20this%20was%20the%20first%20time%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20were%20ready%20to%20fight%20a%20war%20to%20create%20a%20new%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20two%20weeks%20before%20the%20official%20declaration%20of%20war%20on%20December%203%2C%201971%2C%20Indian%20tanks%20silenced%20enemy%20guns%20in%20east%20Pakistan%20in%20the%20Battle%20of%20Garibpur%2C%20a%20preemptive%20strike%20aimed%20to%20hit%20the%20Boyra%20salient%20in%20east%20Pakistan%20following%20continuous%20air%20space%20violations%20and%20artillery%20shelling%20on%20Indian%20villages%20in%20the%20east.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattle%20Of%20Boyra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gnats%20from%2022%20Squadron%2C%20'Swifts'%2C%20of%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20intercepted%20four%20Pakistani%20F-86%20Sabre%20jets%20and%20claimed%20their%20first%20kill%20in%20the%20war%20on%20November%2022%20before%20it%20was%20officially%20declared.%20The%20Pakistani%20Sabres%20from%2014%20Squadron%2C%20the%20'Tail%20Choppers'%2C%20were%20airborne%20to%20provide%20air%20support%20to%20troops%20battling%20in%20Garibpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sabres%20were%20picked%20up%20near%20Jessore%20in%20East%20Pakistan%20(now%20Bangladesh)%20by%20Indian%20radars%20and%20Gnats%20were%20scrambled%20under%20the%20call%20sign%20'Cocktail'%20from%20the%20Dum%20Dum%20airbase%20in%20West%20Bengal%20to%20intercept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGnats%20hold%20a%20special%20place%20in%20Indian%20Air%20Force's%20(IAF)%20history.%20In%201965%2C%20Gnat%2C%20piloted%20by%20Trevor%20Keelor%2C%20from%2023%20Squadron%20shot%20down%20F-86%20Sabres%20over%20Pathankot%20and%20the%20IAF%20claimed%20its%20first-ever%20kill%20post-independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%2014%20Punjab%20(Nabha%20Akal)%20under%20Headquarters%2042%20Infantry%20Brigade%20under%209%20Infantry%20Division%20was%20tasked%20to%20capture%20Garibpur%2C%209%20Km%20east%20of%20Boyra%20salient%2C%20on%20the%20first%20light%20of%20November%2021.%20The%20Nabha%20Akal%20battalion%20under%20the%20command%20of%20Lt%20Col%20RK%20Singh%20was%20supported%20by%2045%20Cavalry's%20'Charlie'%20(C)%20Squadron%20of%20PT-76%20Tanks%2C%20famously%20known%20as%20'Pippa'%2C%20under%20Major%20DS%20Narang's%20command.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20dawn%20broke%20on%20November%2021%2C%20a%20fierce%20battle%20began%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan.%20The%20Indian%20battalion-sized%20deployment%20was%20turning%20on%20Pakistan's%20brigade-sized%20deployment%20which%20was%20supported%20by%20an%20independent%20armoured%20squadron%20and%20Arty%20(Artillery)%2C%20and%20later%20by%20Pak's%20F-86%20Sabre%20fighter%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMURDER%2C%20MURDER%2C%20MURDER!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20IAF%20Gnat%20flown%20by%20Flight%20Lieutenant%20(Flt%20Lt)%20Ganapathy%2C%20Flt%20Lt%20Massey%2C%20Flying%20Officer%20(Fg%20Offr)%20Soares%20and%20Fg%20Offr%20Lazarus%20vectored%20their%20Gnats%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Sabres.%20Fg%20Off%20Bagchi%20was%20in%20command%20of%20the%20radar%20scope.%20Almost%2017%20minutes%20and%20150x30%20mm%20Cannon%20rounds%20later%2C%20the%20IAF%20shot%20down%20a%20Sabre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlt%20Lt%20Ganapathy%20radioed%20-%20%26quot%3BMurder%2C%20Murder%2C%20Murder!%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20first%20Sabre%20was%20shot%20down.%20The%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20shared%20a%20montage%20of%20images%20of%20Sabre%20being%20shot%20down%20by%20the%20Gnat.%20The%20pictures%20were%20taken%20by%20the%20Gun%20Camera%20of%20one%20of%20the%20Gnats.%20Two%20Sabres%20were%20shot%20down%20and%20one%20was%20limping%20towards%20Dacca%20(now%20Dhaka).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMURDER%2C%20MURDER%2C%20MURDER!%20Thus%20was%20announced%20the%20IAF%20drawing%20first%20blood%20on%2022%20Nov%2071.%20Tracking%20raiding%20Sabres%20of%20the%20PAF%2C%20four%20Gnats%20of%2022%20Sqn%20were%20scrambled%20under%20the%20callsign%20%E2%80%98Cocktail'.%20Living%20up%20to%20their%20Sqn's%20name%2C%20the%20Gnats%20got%20airborne%20SWIFT-ly%20at%201451%20hr%20from%20Dum%20Dum.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4Dna2S9wXQ%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4Dna2S9wXQ%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(%40IAF_MCC)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FIAF_MCC%2Fstatus%2F1727152582895018266%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2022%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20on%20the%20ground%20saw%20the%20air%20battle%20of%20Boyra%20and%20the%20four%20IAF%20pilots%20were%20heroes%20of%20Boyra.%20Defence%20Minister%20Jagjivan%20Ram%20garlanded%20the%20Gnat%20pilots%20who%20shot%20down%20the%20Sabres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F1dc9fstg_jagjivan-ram-and-gnat-pilots_625x300_22_November_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sound%20of%20guns%20echoed%20for%20over%207%20hours%20in%20Garibpur.%20When%20guns%20went%20silent%2C%2011%20M-24%20Chaffees%20were%20found%20destroyed%20and%20three%20abandoned%20in%20good%20condition%2C%20while%20the%20victory%20came%20at%20the%20cost%20of%202%20PT-76%20tanks.%20Major%20DS%20Narang%20(Chiefy)%20was%20killed%20in%20action.%20Major%20Narang%20was%20awarded%20the%20Maha%20Vir%20Chakra%20(Posthumously).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrigadier%20Balram%20Mehta%2C%20who%20was%20a%20captain%20back%20then%2C%20has%20written%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20Battle%20of%20Garibpur%20in%20his%20book%20'The%20Burning%20Chaffees'.%20The%20book%20has%20been%20turned%20into%20a%20motion%20picture%20named%20'Pippa'%2C%20which%20was%20released%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700666100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fuodrstao_battle-of-boyra-iaf-1200-_625x300_25_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmurder-murder-murder-when-iaf-gnat-jets-shot-down-3-pak-sabres-in-1971-4597479%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20crisis%20in%20East%20Pakistan%20reached%20a%20climax%20with%20one%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20wars%20fought%20in%20modern%20history%20which%20led%20to%20splitting%20Pakistan%20into%20two%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmurder-murder-murder-when-iaf-gnat-jets-shot-down-3-pak-sabres-in-1971-4597479%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmurder-murder-murder-when-iaf-gnat-jets-shot-down-3-pak-sabr