tps%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhindustan-zinc-expected-to-have-stable-performance-in-coming-quarters-ceo-123112201037_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDidn't%20Give%20False%20Ads%2C%20Ready%20For%20Death%20Sentence%20If%20Guilty%26quot%3B%3A%20Patanjali%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EYoga%20teacher%20Ramdev-led%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20it%20was%20not%20making%20any%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20advertisements%20or%20propaganda%26quot%3B%20regarding%20its%20products%2C%20and%20said%20it%20would%20not%20object%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20were%20to%20impose%20a%20fine%20or%20%26quot%3Beven%20give%20us%20a%20death%20sentence%26quot%3B%20if%20found%20making%20misleading%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20cautioned%20the%20company%20against%20making%20%26quot%3Bfalse%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%26quot%3B%20claims%20in%20advertisements%20about%20its%20medicines%20as%20cure%20of%20several%20diseases%2C%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20said%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bdatabase%20with%20more%20than%20one%20crore%20people%2C%20with%20real%20world%20evidence%2C%20preclinical%20and%20clinical%20evidence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPatanjali%20have%20made%20thousands%20of%20people%20free%20from%20several%20diseases%20like%20BP%2C%20sugar%2C%20thyroid%2C%20asthma%2C%20arthritis%2C%20obesity%2C%20liver%20and%20kidney%20failure%2C%20and%20cancer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20humbly%20respect%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20and%20if%20we%20make%20false%20advertisements%20or%20propaganda%2C%20we%20would%20not%20have%20any%20objections%20if%20honourable%20court%20imposes%20a%20fine%20of%20crores%20or%20even%20give%20us%20a%20death%20sentence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20bench%20comprising%20Justice%20Ahsanuddin%20Amanullah%20and%20Justice%20Prashant%20Kumar%20Mishra%20orally%20observed%20while%20hearing%20a%20plea%20of%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20such%20false%20and%20misleading%20advertisements%20of%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20have%20to%20stop%20immediately.%20The%20court%20will%20take%20any%20such%20infraction%20very%20seriously...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%2C%20on%20August%2023%2C%202022%2C%20had%20issued%20notices%20to%20the%20Union%20health%20ministry%20and%20Ministry%20of%20Ayush%20and%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20Ltd%2C%20on%20the%20plea%20of%20the%20IMA%20alleging%20a%20smear%20campaign%20by%20Ramdev%20against%20the%20vaccination%20drive%20and%20modern%20medicines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20statement%2C%20Patanjali%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20would%20like%20emphasise%20that%20we%20are%20not%20spreading%20any%20false%20propaganda.%20Hundreds%20of%20therapies%20of%20Yoga%2C%20Ayurveda%2C%20Naturopathy%2C%20Panchakarma%2C%20Shatkarma%2C%20fasting%20and%20with%20the%20integrated%20treatment%20of%20system%2C%20we%20have%20made%20thousands%20of%20people%20free%20from%20several%20diseases%20like%20BP%2C%20sugar%2C%20thyroid%2C%20asthma%2C%20arthritis%2C%20obesity%2C%20liver%20and%20kidney%20failure%2C%20and%20cancer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20claimed%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20the%20world's%20best%20research%20centre%20on%20ayurveda%2C%20Patanjali%20Research%20Foundation%2C%20for%20research%20on%20traditional%20treatment%20and%20sanatan%20knowledge%20tradition.%20Where%20hundreds%20of%20world%20renowned%20scientists%20are%20conducting%20research%2C%20and%20by%20following%20more%20than%203%2C000%20research%20protocols%2C%20close%20to%20500%20research%20papers%20have%20been%20published%20in%20the%20world's%20highly%20reputed%20research%20journals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20accused%20%26quot%3Bsome%20stubborn%20and%20so-called%20frustrated%20doctors%20of%20the%20medical%20sector%2C%20who%20oppose%20Yoga%2C%20Ayurveda%20and%20Naturopathy%26quot%3B%20of%20have%20a%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20acknowledging%20that%20diseases%20can%20be%20controlled%20with%20synthetic%20medicines%2C%20it%20said%20%26quot%3Bbut%20cannot%20be%20cured%26quot%3B%2C%20this%20problem%20of%20allopathy%20is%20not%20a%20problem%20for%20Yoga-Ayurveda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20medical%20field%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20many%20modern%20practitioners%20those%20who%20are%20committing%20medical%20crimes%20by%20installing%20fake%20pacemakers%2C%20stealing%20kidneys%2C%20taking%20unnecessary%20medicines%20and%20conducting%20tests%20indiscriminately%20as%20medical%20mafia%2Fdrug%20mafia%2C%20we%20have%20fought%20against%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700665080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2Fje5130c_ramdev-patanjali-reuters_625x300_12_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdidnt-give-false-ads-ready-for-death-sentence-if-guilty-says-baba-ramdev-patanjali-after-supreme-court-hearing-4597406%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Yoga%20teacher%20Ramdev-led%20Patanjali%20Ayurved%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20it%20was%20not%20making%20any%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20advertisements%20or%20propaganda%26quot%3B%20regarding%20its%20products%2C%20and%20said%20it%20would%20not%20object%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20were%20to%20impose%20a%20fine%20or%20%26quot%3Beven%20give%20us%20a%20death%20sentence%26quot%3B%20if%20found%20making%20misleading%20claims.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdidnt-give-false-ads-ready-for-death-sentence-if-guilty-says-baba-ramdev-patanjali-after-supreme-court-hearing-4597406%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fdidnt-give-false-ads-ready-for-death-sentence-if-guilty-says-baba-ramdev-patanjali-after-supreme-court-hearing-4597406%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl