2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%E2%80%9D%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20this%20month%2C%20but%20can%20it%20follow%20through%20with%20due%20process%20and%20actually%20do%20its%20job%3F%20CERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20is%20to%20provide%20response%20to%20computer%20emergencies%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%20It%20has%20never%20delivered%20on%20this%20promise%20and%20has%20become%20yet%20another%20government%20agency%20sleeping%20on%20its%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20notifications%20sent%20by%20Apple%20to%20several%20Members%20of%20Parliament%2C%20politicians%2C%20journalists%20and%20others%20has%20raised%20concerns%20yet%20again%20of%20unregulated%20surveillance%20activities%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20intelligence%20agencies.%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20security%20notifications%20point%20towards%20state-sponsored%20actors%20and%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20argument%2C%20could%20mean%20any%20nation%20state%20including%20an%20enemy%20state%20out%20there%2C%20making%20it%20a%20classic%20case%20of%20computer%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20390px)%2085vw%2C%20390px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22390%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F23161125%2FTerminal-column-logo-300x209.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-637305%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22272%5C%22%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(MeitY)%20has%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20Apple%20asking%20the%20firm%20to%20cooperate%20with%20CERT-IN%20and%20Apple%20has%20co-operated%20by%20bringing%20in%20its%20experts%20to%20work%20with%20CERT-IN.%20CERT-IN%20guidelines%20mandate%20that%20every%20organisation%20must%20report%20security%20incidents%20within%20six%20hours%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20Apple%20was%20reminded%20of%20this.%20Apple%20clearly%20has%20not%20followed%20this%2C%20violating%20some%20of%20CERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECERT-IN%20similarly%20sent%20notices%20to%20WhatsApp%20in%202019%2C%20when%20WhatsApp%20alerted%20select%20individuals%20of%20being%20targeted%20by%20Pegasus.%20WhatsApp%20notified%20CERT-IN%20about%20the%20security%20issue%20in%20its%20systems%20without%20giving%20further%20details%20of%20people%20early%20into%20its%20incident%20response%2C%20even%20before%20it%20notified%20people%20who%20were%20affected.%20CERT-IN%20did%20not%20follow%20through%20on%20the%20issue%20until%20the%20scale%20of%20it%20was%20publicly%20disclosed%20by%20WhatsApp.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news-technology%2Fgovt-investigating-whether-china-linked-agencies-are-behind-apple-spyware-attack-9032714%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20investigation%20into%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20security%20notifications%20pointed%20out%20how%20CERT-IN%20is%20now%20investigating%20Chinese%20government-linked%20agencies%2C%20as%20the%20place%20of%20production%20of%20most%20iPhones%20is%20China.%20CERT-IN%20is%20now%20investigating%20which%20nation%20state%20actor%20could%20be%20behind%20these%20attacks%2C%20while%20the%20minister%20for%20electronics%20and%20information%20technology%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fcentre-reacts-to-oppositions-hacking-claim-says-compulsive-critics-want-to-distract-indian-people%2Farticleshow%2F104850753.cms%5C%22%3Edenied%20it%20could%20be%20Indian%20agencies%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rubbished%20the%20opposition%20for%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20past%20actions%20show%20us%20that%20these%20notices%20that%20it%20issues%20to%20private%20companies%20have%20never%20been%20translated%20into%20any%20meaningful%20regulatory%20actions.%20Neither%20did%20CERT-IN%20follow%20through%20with%20WhatsApp%20about%20Pegasus%2C%20nor%20did%20it%20carry%20out%20an%20independent%20investigation%20which%20most%20cyber%20security%20agencies%20in%20different%20countries%20carried%20out.%20As%20a%20regulatory%20body%20responsible%20for%20cyber%20security%2C%20CERT-IN%20has%20never%20investigated%20any%20data%20breaches%2C%20nor%20has%20it%20provided%20any%20actual%20incident%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Seizing%20Devices%20Needs%20Due%20Process.%20So%20Does%20Remote%20Accessing%20Via%20Spyware%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdevice-seizures-guidelines-rules-procedures%5C%22%3ESeizing%20Devices%20Needs%20Due%20Process.%20So%20Does%20Remote%20Accessing%20Via%20Spyware%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bureaucratic%20body%20under%20MeitY%2C%20CERT-IN%20is%20clearly%20not%20an%20independent%20institution%20and%20has%20no%20history%20of%20actually%20conducting%20serious%20forensic%20audits.%20The%20organisational%20capacity%20to%20even%20conduct%20an%20investigation%20necessary%20for%20state-sponsored%20attacks%20is%20probably%20not%20available%20to%20CERT-IN.%20Most%20of%20CERT-IN%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20is%20within%20India%E2%80%99s%20privately%20regulated%20cybersecurity%20industry.%20CERT-IN%20decides%20who%20can%20conduct%20cybersecurity%20audits%20by%20empanelling%20private%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20digital%20evidence%20perspective%2C%20no%20private%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20forensics%20are%20considered%20valid%20unless%20that%20organisation%20is%20empanelled%20by%20CERT-IN.%20This%20gives%20CERT-IN%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20more%20power%20to%20reject%20any%20forensic%20evidence%20just%20because%20the%20organisations%20%E2%80%98can%E2%80%99t%20be%20trusted%E2%80%99.%20Even%20if%20Apple%20provides%20evidence%20there%20were%20indeed%20state-sponsored%20attacks%2C%20with%20no%20actual%20conclusive%20proofs%20attributing%20exact%20actors%2C%20Indian%20authorities%20are%20likely%20to%20reject%20it%20or%20deflect%20the%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20been%20a%20long%20pending%20demand%20for%20CERT-IN%20to%20actually%20conduct%20forensic%20investigations%20of%20cyber%20incidents%20and%20to%20publish%20its%20findings.%20The%20only%20major%20reports%20that%20are%20published%20by%20CERT-IN%20are%20its%20annual%20reports%20with%20details%20of%20its%20activities%20like%20training%20and%20workshops%20it%20has%20conducted.%20As%20a%20cybersecurity%20regulator%2C%20CERT-IN%20is%20as%20bad%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20regulators%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20no%20interest%20in%20seriously%20regulating%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20sake%20of%20argument%2C%20if%20it%20were%20indeed%20Chinese%20actors%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20targeting%20the%20Indian%20opposition%20and%20journalists%2C%20even%20then%20CERT-IN%20has%20no%20capacity%20to%20respond%20to%20this.%20The%20National%20Critical%20Information%20Infrastructure%20Protection%20Centre%20(NCIIPC)%2C%20a%20unit%20of%20the%20National%20Technical%20Research%20Organisation%20(NTRO)%2C%20has%20relatively%20more%20experience%20in%20tackling%20nation%20state%20actors%20targeting%20our%20critical%20infrastructure.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20cybersecurity%2C%20NCIIPC%20still%20responds%20to%20threats%20and%20provides%20incident%20response%2C%20which%20CERT-IN%20has%20largely%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20CERT-IN%20is%20basically%20a%20regulatory%20organisation%20responsible%20for%20directing%20the%20industry%20to%20adopt%20cybersecurity%20practices%2C%20NCIIPC%20is%20more%20of%20a%20hands-on%20organisation%20that%20has%20in-house%20capacity%20to%20handle%20threats.%20If%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20really%20serious%20about%20addressing%20nation%20state%20actors%20targeting%20Indians%20and%20is%20concerned%20with%20the%20safety%20of%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20and%20others%2C%20it%20would%20comprehensively%20address%20this%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Apple%20Is%20Not%20the%20First%20Tech%20Company%20To%20Allege%20Government%20Role%20in%20Misuse%20of%20Spyware%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fapple-tech-company-allege-government-role-spyware-misuse%5C%22%3EApple%20Is%20Not%20the%20First%20Tech%20Company%20To%20Allege%20Government%20Role%20in%20Misuse%20of%20Spyware%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20needs%20more%20transparency%20on%20how%20its%20security%20apparatus%20and%20its%20regulators%20operate.%20This%20is%20unlikely%20to%20happen%20by%20itself%20and%20with%20the%20parliament%20and%20its%20committees%20unable%20to%20function%20under%20the%20current%20political%20climate%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20wait%20for%20political%20change.%20One%20could%20only%20hope%20that%20actually%20happens%20and%20the%20situation%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20worse%20with%20the%20usage%20of%20state%20surveillance%20against%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20people%20who%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20this%20and%20want%20more%20answers%20from%20Apple%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20to%20be%20revealed%20in%20India.%20If%20one%20is%20looking%20to%20follow%20through%20on%20this%20and%20want%20Apple%20to%20provide%20more%20details%2C%20they%20should%20legally%20proceed%20against%20Apple%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20Any%20litigation%20around%20this%20in%20India%20is%20unlikely%20to%20result%20in%20any%20positive%20response%20from%20any%20of%20the%20actors.%20Apple%20sued%20the%20NSO%20Group%20in%20the%20US%20for%20targeting%20its%20users%20and%20to%20curb%20abuse%20of%20nation%20state%20actors.%20If%20Apple%20is%20really%20serious%20about%20the%20privacy%20of%20its%20users%2C%20it%20will%20respond%20positively%20and%20give%20further%20details%2C%20but%20may%20be%20unlikely%20to%20do%20so%20in%20India%20with%20pressure%20from%20Indian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700659812000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F05194313%2FIMG_4672.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fwhy-cert-ins-investigation-into-apple-security-notifications-is-going-nowhere%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bureaucratic%20body%20under%20MeitY%2C%20CERT-IN%20is%20clearly%20not%20an%20independent%20institution%20and%20has%20no%20history%20of%20actually%20conducting%20serious%20forensic%20audits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fwhy-cert-ins-investigation-into-apple-security-notifications-is-going-nowhere%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20foiled%20plot%20to%20kill%20Sikh%20separatist%20Pannun%20on%20American%20soil%2C%20reports%20FT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700659651000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fmisc%2F2023-11%2F22%2Ffull%2F20230925191L.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-foiled-plot-to-kill-sikh-separatist-pannun-on-american-soil-reports-ft-123112200889_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Following%20the%20murder%20of%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%2C%20a%20Canadian%20Sikh%20separatist%20assassinated%20in%20Vancouver%20in%20June%2C%20the%20US%20alerted%20several%20allies%20about%20the%20plot%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-foiled-plot-to-kill-sikh-separatist-pannun-on-american-soil-reports-ft-123112200889_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fus-foiled-plot-to-kill-sikh-separatist-pannun-on-american-soil-reports-ft-123112200889_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findia-news%2Fus-foiled-plot-to-kill-sikh-separatist-pannun-on-american-soil-reports-ft-123112200889_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Obama's%20Former%20Advisor%20Apologises%20After%20Video%20Of%20Racist%20Rant%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20former%20US%20State%20Department%20employee%20and%20national%20security%20official%2C%20identified%20as%20Stuart%20Seldowitz%2C%20was%20captured%20on%20video%20engaging%20in%20harassment%20of%20a%20halal%20food%20vendor%20in%20Manhattan.%20The%20viral%20footage%20shows%20him%20taking%20pictures%20of%20the%20vendor%20and%20directing%20hateful%20Islamophobic%20comments%20towards%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20brief%20exchange%20about%20child%20casualties%2C%20Seldowitz%20callously%20remarks%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20killed%204%2C000%20Palestinian%20kids%2C%20you%20know%20what%3F%20It%20wasn't%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20series%20of%20disturbing%20videos%20online%20where%20Seldowitz%20is%20seen%20hurling%20a%20barrage%20of%20anti-Palestine%20comments%20and%20insults%20at%20the%20unidentified%20vendor.%20One%20video%20shows%20Seldowitz%20accosting%20the%20vendor%2C%20calling%20him%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%26quot%3B%20and%20making%20inflammatory%20remarks%20about%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3Ehis%20harassment%20of%20the%20Halal%20Cart%20vendor%20at%2083rd%20and%202nd%20ave%20has%20been%20ongoing%20for%20two%20weeks.%3Cbr%3E%5CnNYPD%20has%20been%20called%20multiple%20times%2C%20local%20precinct%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20nothing%20they%20can%20do%20because%20it%20is%20free%20speech%E2%80%9D.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F6LYL40TTFK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F6LYL40TTFK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Layla%20%F0%9F%AA%AC%20(%40itslaylas)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fitslaylas%2Fstatus%2F1727080775516819782%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Seldowitz%20later%20regretted%20his%20statement%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20phone%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F11%2F21%2Fnyregion%2Fseldowitz-vendor-islamophobia-nyc.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20had%20not%20seen%20the%20videos.%20The%20episodes%20started%20after%20he%20asked%20the%20vendor%20if%20he%20was%20Egyptian.%20As%20the%20conversation%20progressed%2C%20the%20man%20expressed%20support%20for%20Hamas%2C%20Seldowitz%20said%2C%20though%20no%20such%20claims%20are%20captured%20in%20any%20of%20the%20videos%20that%20have%20been%20made%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20point%2C%20I%20got%20rather%20upset%2C%20and%20I've%20said%20things%20to%20him%20that%2C%20in%20retrospect%2C%20I%20probably%20regret%2C%20though%E2%80%94that%20I%20do%20regret%2C%E2%80%9D%20Seldowitz%20said.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20focusing%20on%20him%20and%20what%20he%20said%2C%20I%20expanded%20into%20insulting%20his%20religion%20and%20so%20on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthehill.com%2Fhomenews%2F4322188-lobbying-firm-former-obama-adviser-anti-palestinian-comments%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hill%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gotham%20Government%20Relations%2C%20a%20DC-based%20lobbying%20firm%2C%20has%20reportedly%20cut%20ties%20with%20Stuart%20Seldowitz%20who%20was%20a%20former%20Obama%20administration%20adviser.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGotham%20Government%20Relations%20has%20ended%20all%20affiliation%20with%20Stuart%20Seldowitz%2C%20an%20individual%20who%20hasn't%20contributed%20to%20our%20work%20in%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lobbying%20firm%20said%20Tuesday%20on%20X%2C%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22zxx%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FyzGDazC5GY%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FyzGDazC5GY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Gotham%20Government%20Relations%20(%40GothamGovt)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGothamGovt%2Fstatus%2F1727042234518995357%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2021%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20outlet%20further%20said%20that%20Seldowitz%20served%20as%20the%20acting%20director%20for%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20South%20Asia%20Directorate%20under%20the%20Obama%20administration%2C%20according%20to%20his%20Gotham%20Government%20Relations%20bio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20hired%20by%20the%20lobbying%20firm%20last%20year%20as%20its%20foreign%20affairs%20chair%2C%20according%20to%20a%20news%20release.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHis%20comments%20come%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20a%20spike%20in%20anti-semitism%20and%20Islamophobia%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700659560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fn9v45th_stuart-seldowitz_625x300_22_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fobamas-former-advisor-apologises-after-video-of-racist-rant-goes-viral-4597143%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20viral%20video%20shows%20Stuart%20Seldowitz%20asking%20the%20food%20vendor%20racist%20and%20Islamophobic%20questions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fobamas-former-advisor-apologises-after-video-of-racist-rant-goes-viral-4597143%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fobamas-former-advisor-apologises-after-video-of-racist-rant-goes-viral-4597143%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fobamas-former-advisor-apologises-after-video-of-racist-rant-goes-viral-4597143%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Not%20In%20The%20Race%20To%20Be%20Chief%20Minister%3A%20Rajasthan%20BJP%20Chief%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20BJP's%20state%20unit%20chief%20CP%20Joshi%2C%20seen%20as%20a%20strong%20contender%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20post%2C%20has%20ruled%20himself%20out%20of%20the%20race.%20In%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Mr%20Joshi%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Blooking%20forward%20to%20putting%20the%20first%20garland%20on%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Rajasthan%20if%20the%20BJP%20comes%20to%20power%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Joshi%2C%20always%20mild-mannered%2C%20was%20sharp%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post%20that%20has%20intrigued%20many%20in%20absence%20of%20the%20BJP%20failing%20to%20announce%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20post.%20Speculation%20peaked%20as%20the%20party%20fielded%20several%20leaders%20who%20do%20not%20see%20eye-to-eye%20with%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20the%20last%20BJP%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20the%20state.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Raje%20has%20not%20been%20given%20any%20assurance%20about%20being%20the%20candidate%20for%20the%20top%20job%2C%20leading%20many%20to%20conclude%20that%20she%20has%20fallen%20foul%20of%20the%20party's%20central%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20is%20the%20question%20of%20CM%20post%20coming%20up%3F%20The%20party%20has%20made%20it%20a%20rule%20that%20no%20Chief%20Ministerial%20candidate%20will%20be%20announced%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Joshi%20told%20NDTV%20today.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20question%20of%20having%20a%20CM%20face%20for%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20should%20not%20arise.%20The%20BJP's%20parliamentary%20board%20has%20decided%20it%20will%20not%20fight%20the%20elections%20on%20a%20CM%20face.%20It%20has%20not%20fought%20the%20election%20on%20a%20cm%20face%20in%20Karnataka%20or%20Goa%2C%20so%20why%20should%20the%20question%20arise%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Joshi%2C%2048%2C%20was%20given%20charge%20of%20the%20state%20unit%20early%20this%20March%2C%20when%20it%20vied%20with%20the%20Congress%20in%20making%20headlines%20over%20factionalism.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20been%20credited%20with%20bringing%20together%20the%20rival%20factions%20and%20crafting%20a%20cohesive%20campaign%20that%20focuses%20on%20alleged%20anti-incumbency%20and%20Congress's%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20Congress%20campaign%2C%20Mr%20Joshi%20questioned%20today%20why%20the%20party%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20five%20years%20to%20come%20up%20with%20its%20guarantees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Congress%20government%20should%20have%20given%20their%20guarantees%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20contending%20that%20the%20party%20is%20yet%20to%20fulfil%20its%20earlier%20promises.%20As%20examples%2C%20he%20cited%20the%20promise%20of%20one%20crore%20mobile%20phones.%20%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20only%2017%20lakh%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajasthan%20goes%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2025%20and%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20will%20take%20place%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700659260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F2d8iglfc_cp-joshi_625x300_22_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajathan-assembly-elections-not-in-the-race-to-be-chief-minister-rajasthan-bjp-chief-to-ndtv-4597054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajasthan%20BJP's%20state%20unit%20chief%20CP%20Joshi%2C%20seen%20