20an%20important%20pedestal%20in%20one's%20career.%20Attending%20college%20and%20studying%20is%20important%20for%20several%20reasons-%20it%20gives%20an%20individual%20a%20better%20opportunity%20in%20future%2C%20helps%20in%20skill%20development%2C%20aids%20all-round%20learning%2C%20boosts%20self-confidence%20and%20personal%20growth%20and%20so%20on.%20However%2C%20a%20Chief%20Executive%20Officer%20of%20a%20%24100%20million%20company%20recently%20stated%20that%20the%20classes%20she%20took%20at%20college%20don't%20help%20her%20at%20her%20workplace%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F11%2F14%2Fslutty-vegan-ceo-pinky-cole-on-the-value-of-college-networking.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECNBC%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Pinky%20Cole%2C%2035%2C%20is%20the%20Chief%20of%20Slutty%20Vegan%2C%20a%20US-based%20burger%20chain%20with%20locations%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20graduated%20with%20a%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20mass%20media%20arts%20from%20Clark%20Atlanta%20University%20in%202009.%20Talking%20about%20her%20college%2C%20the%20CEO%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20going%20to%20be%20totally%20transparent%20with%20you.%20When%20I%20went%20to%20college%2C%20all%20the%20stuff%20that%20I%20learned%2C%20I%20don't%20remember%20(any)%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20do%20remember%20is%20the%20relationships%20that%20I%20built%20along%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%20Delta%20Sigma%20Theta%2C%20Ms%20Cole's%20college%20mate%2C%20had%20a%20significant%20influence%20on%20the%20development%20of%20her%20professionalism%20and%20leadership%20abilities.%20He%20gave%20her%20professional%20and%20leadership%20skills%20training%20as%20well%20as%20connections%20to%20people%20she%20%26quot%3Bstill%20connects%20with%20to%20this%20day.%26quot%3B%20She%20added%20that%20since%20%26quot%3Bwe've%20already%20built%20a%20rapport%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20seeks%20out%20new%20connections%20with%20former%20students%20she%20runs%20into%20at%20events%20and%20business%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20who%20I%20went%20to%20school%20with%20are%20now%20executives%20and%20CEOs%20of%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20companies%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20able%20to%20build%20those%20relationships%20before%20they%20became%20these%20big-time%20executives.%20So%20the%20relationship%20is%20organic%2C%20it's%20authentic%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20her%20experience%20at%20college%20was%20worth%20it%20and%20she%20would%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%20if%20given%20a%20choice.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20could%20turn%20back%20the%20hands%20of%20time%2C%20I%20would%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%20...%20spend%20%24200%2C000%20to%20go%20to%20school%2C%20to%20make%20some%20relationships%20and%20network%20with%20those%20people.%20Because%20guess%20what%2C%20your%20network%20is%20your%20net%20worth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20advised%20young%20entrepreneurs%20and%20said%20strong%20relationships%20formed%20during%20college%20will%20be%20there%20for%20a%20lifetime.%20%26quot%3BBy%20all%20means%2C%20I%20believe%20that%20you%20should%20go%2C%20because%20the%20relationships%2C%20if%20nothing%20else%2C%20will%20be%20the%20thing%20that%20will%20support%20and%20carry%20you%20(on%20your%20career%20journey)%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Cole%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700658960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fshotrggo_pinky-cole_625x300_22_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdont-remember-any-of-it-ceo-of-100-million-us-company-on-college-education-4597116%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20added%20that%20her%20experience%20at%20college%20was%20worth%20it%20and%20she%20would%20do%20it%20all%20over%20again%20if%20given%20a%20choice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-