%20respected%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20BJP%20is%20committed%20to%20fulfil%20these%20announcements.%20The%20history%20of%20BJP%20is%20witness%20to%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Congress%20Party%20has%20become%20synonymous%20with%20five%20things%20in%20five%20years.%20First%20%E2%80%93%20corruption.%20Second%20%E2%80%93%20insult%20to%20sisters%2C%20daughters%20and%20mothers.%20Third%20%E2%80%93%20contempt%20of%20farmers.%20Fourth%20%E2%80%93%20atrocities%20against%20the%20poor.%20Fifth%20%E2%80%93%20playing%20with%20the%20future%20of%20youth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20said%20that%20it%20has%20already%20fulfilled%20over%2090%25%20of%20the%20promises%20made%20in%20its%202018%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20fulfilled%2096%25%20of%20our%20manifesto%20because%20our%20motto%20as%20Kharge%3Cem%3E%20ji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Rahul%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20say%20is%20that%20don%E2%80%99t%20make%20promises%20and%20if%20you%20do%2C%20then%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20fulfilled%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20while%20releasing%20the%20manifesto%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20November%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20has%20made%20corruption%20in%20the%20Congress%20government%2C%20lack%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%2C%20and%20paper%20leaks%20major%20poll%20issues%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20looking%20to%20buck%20the%20trend%20of%20revolving%20door%20elections%20in%20the%20state%20and%20make%20a%20comeback%20riding%20on%20its%20flagship%20schemes%20for%20social%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20look%20at%20how%20the%20poll%20documents%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20compares%20on%20key%20issues%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPromises%20to%20farmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20immediate%20priorities%20after%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20bring%20a%20law%20to%20implement%20the%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20following%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20recommendations%2C%20interest-free%20loans%20up%20to%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20all%20farmers%20from%20cooperative%20banks%2C%20withdraw%20pending%20cases%20against%20farmers%20in%20connection%20with%20their%20participation%20in%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%20additional%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20to%20farmers%20under%20the%20PM%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%2C%20free%20education%20to%20farmers%E2%80%99%20children%2C%20an%20additional%20bonus%20of%20Rs%202%2C700%20per%20quintal%20over%20the%20MSP%20on%20wheat%2C%20along%20with%20providing%20MSP%20on%20jowar%20and%20bajra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENadda%20while%20releasing%20the%20manifesto%20accused%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20snatching%20lands%20from%2019%2C400%20farmers%2C%20and%20promised%20to%20compensate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGehlot%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20said%20that%20a%20commission%20headed%20by%20a%20high%20court%20judge%20will%20be%20constituted%20to%20look%20into%20cases%20where%20farmers%E2%80%99%20lands%20have%20been%20seized.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEastern%20Rajasthan%20Canal%20Project%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Eastern%20Rajasthan%20Canal%20Project%20(ERCP)%20has%20become%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20seeks%20to%20address%20water%20scarcity%20in%20Eastern%20Rajasthan%20by%20diverting%20water%20from%20the%20Chambal%20basin.%20The%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fmodi-failed-to-fulfil-promise-of-granting-national-project-status-to-eastern-rajasthan-canal-project-cong%2F1853935%2F%5C%22%3Enot%20giving%20national%20status%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20project%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20accused%20the%20state%20government%20of%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fpolitics%2Fgehlot-responsible-for-stalling-east-rajasthan-canal-project-rathore-123101700003_1.html%5C%22%3E%20stalling%20the%20project.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20introduce%20a%20Detailed%20Plan%20for%20the%20Staggered%20Implementation%20of%20the%20Eastern%20Rajasthan%20Canal%20Project%20(ERCP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20too%20has%20promised%20to%20implement%20the%20project%20in%20a%20time-bound%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorruption%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20made%20the%20alleged%20corruption%20by%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20one%20of%20its%20main%20poll%20planks%2C%20has%20promised%20to%20constitute%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20(SIT)%20to%20look%20into%20exam%20paper%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20form%20another%20SIT%20to%20look%20into%20fertiliser%2C%20mid-day%20meal%2C%20mining%2C%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana%2C%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%20and%20other%20alleged%20scams%20and%20bring%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20bring%20out%20a%20White%20Paper%20listing%20all%20instances%20of%20corruption%20by%20the%20Gehlot%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%20leaks%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20implement%20%E2%80%9Cmeasures%20and%20stringent%20punishments%20to%20curb%20incidents%20of%20paper%20leaks%20for%20competitive%20exams.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGehlot%20said%20that%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20make%20an%20issue%20out%20of%20exam%20paper%20leaks%2C%20nowhere%20in%20the%20country%20is%20there%20a%20more%20stringent%20law%20than%20Rajasthan%20on%20paper%20leaks%20which%20includes%20life%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20charge%20on%20the%20lack%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20install%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20public%20places%2C%20security%20guards%20in%20every%20village%20and%20urban%20wards%2C%20and%20reduce%20the%20average%20time%20taken%20to%20investigate%20sexual%20harassment%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F02152935%2FScreen-Shot-2020-07-02-at-3.25.07-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221001%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F02152935%2FScreen-Shot-2020-07-02-at-3.25.07-PM.png%201001w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F07%2F02152935%2FScreen-Shot-2020-07-02-at-3.25.07-PM-300x162.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-464247%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22541%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERepresentational%20image.%20Rajasthan%20women.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20it%20has%20also%20set%20a%20target%20to%20increase%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20police%20force%20to%2033%25%20and%20reservations%20for%20gender%20minorities%20in%20police%20recruitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20install%20CCTV%20cameras%20for%20women%E2%80%99s%20safety%20along%20with%2033%25%20reservation%20for%20women%20in%20the%20police%20force%20along%20with%20the%20formation%20of%20three%20women%20battalions%20in%20the%20Rajasthan%20Armed%20Constabulary%20(RAC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20that%20a%20women%E2%80%99s%20police%20station%20will%20be%20opened%20in%20every%20district%2C%20a%20women%E2%80%99s%20desk%20will%20be%20opened%20in%20every%20police%20station%2C%20and%20an%20anti-Romeo%20squad%20will%20be%20formed%20in%20every%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20speedy%20resolution%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20cases%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20form%20fast-track%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20head%20for%20women%20head%20of%20households%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20announced%20Lado%20Protsahan%20Yojana%20that%20it%20will%20provide%20a%20savings%20bond%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20for%20a%20girl%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELPG%20cylinders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20counter%20the%20Congress%20on%20cheaper%20LPG%20cylinders%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%20them%20at%20Rs%20450%20to%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20in%20its%20manifesto%20has%20said%20that%20while%20the%20state%20government%20at%20present%20provides%20cylinders%20at%20Rs%20500%20they%20will%20decrease%20it%20further%20to%20Rs%20400%20if%20voted%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20it%20will%20extend%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20affordable%20LPG%20cylinder%20scheme%2C%20priced%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20to%20families%20under%20the%20NFSA%20(National%20Food%20Security%20Act)%20and%20BPL%20(Below%20Poverty%20Line)%20categories%E2%80%9D%20and%20commit%20to%20further%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20gas%20cylinders%20to%20Rs%20400%20for%20Ujjwala%2C%20NFSA%2C%20and%20BPL%20families%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYouth%20and%20employment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%2010%20lakh%20employment%20opportunities%20including%204%20lakh%20in%20the%20government%20sector%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%202.5%20lakh%20government%20jobs%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20promised%20a%20new%20scheme%20for%20the%20recruitment%20of%20youngsters%20at%20the%20panchayat%20level%2C%20gradually%20merging%20with%20government%20vacancies.%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20start%20a%20toll-free%20call%20centre%20and%20an%20e-Employment%20Exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F10%2F07134348%2FUntitled-design-2021-10-07T134329.195-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-556745%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUnemployed%20youth%20protesting%20against%20irregularities%20which%20took%20place%20in%20government%20exams%20under%20Rajasthan%20Ekikrat%20Berozgaar%20Mahasangh.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FUpen%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20promised%202.5%20lakh%20jobs%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20youth%20it%20has%20promised%20to%20set%20up%20a%20Rajasthan%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Rajasthan%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%93%20modelled%20on%20AIIMS%20and%20IITs%20%E2%80%93%20in%20each%20division%2C%20among%20several%20other%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20rural%20jobs%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20increase%20employment%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20to%20150%20days%20of%20guaranteed%20work%20from%20125%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20free%20English%20medium%20education%20to%20girls%20and%20boys%20and%20to%20bring%20an%20education%20guarantee%20law%20in%20the%20state%20and%20provide%20free%20education%20till%20class%2012%20as%20opposed%20to%20class%208%20under%20RTE%20(Right%20to%20Education).%20It%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20provide%20first-year%20students%20of%20government%20colleges%20with%20a%20free%20laptop%2Ftablet%20upon%20admission%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20promised%20free%20education%20from%20KG%20to%20PG%20to%20poor%20families%20and%20annual%20assistance%20of%20Rs%2012%2C000%20for%20students%20of%20poor%20families%20to%20purchase%20school%20bags%2C%20books%20and%20uniforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20promised%20Free%20Scooty%20Scheme%2C%20arrangements%20will%20be%20made%20to%20give%20free%20scooty%20to%20meritorious%20girl%20students%20after%20passing%20class%2012th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20government%20already%20operates%20a%20scheme%20in%20the%20state%20to%20provide%20scooters%20to%20students%20under%20the%20Kalibai%20Bhil%20Medhavi%20Chhatra%20Scooty%20Yojana%20to%20meritorious%20girl%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealth%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20double%20the%20coverage%20under%20its%20flagship%20health%20insurance%20scheme-the%20Mukhyamantri%20Nishulk%20Chiranjeevi%20Swasthya%20Bima%20Yojana%20from%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20scheme%20it%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20increase%20the%20facilities%20under%20free%20OPD%2FIPD%20in%20government%20medical%20institutions%20at%20the%20district%20and%20block%20level%20and%20include%20IVF%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20recognise%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20profound%20emotional%20and%20social%20challenges%20faced%20by%20couples%20deprived%20of%20the%20joy%20of%20parenthood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20on%20the%20other%