.%20Free%20coupons%20will%20also%20be%20provided%20for%20free%20travel%20for%20women%20in%20state-owned%20buses%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESmartphones%20with%20free%20internet%20will%20also%20be%20given%20to%20women%20heads%20of%20families%20covered%20under%20Mukgyamantri%20Nishulak%20Chiranjeevi%20Swasthya%20Bima%20Yojana%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20also%20plans%20to%20target%20women%20farmers%20to%20encourage%20homestead%20gardens%20and%20horticulture%2C%20recognising%20their%20crucial%20role%20in%20agriculture.%20Women%2C%20it%20has%20promised%2C%20will%20also%20get%2033%25%20reservation%20in%20cooperative%20institutions%2C%20championing%20gender%20equality%20in%20cooperative%20governance.%20Women%20representatives%20will%20be%20empowered%20with%20essential%20skills%2C%20including%20financial%20literacy%2C%20and%20recognise%20and%20incentivise%20best-performing%20women-led%20Gram%20Panchayats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20Grameen%20Aajeevika%20Vikas%20Parishad%20or%20women-centric%20financial%20institution%20will%20give%20subsidised%3C%2Fspan%3E%20loans%20to%20women%20through%20Cluster%20Level%20Federations%20(CLFs)%20and%20benefit%2030%20lakh%20households%20through%20agriculture%20and%20livestock%20programmes%2C%20Congress%20has%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20will%20also%20introduce%20a%20leadership%20course%20to%20promote%20the%20emergence%20of%20next-generation%20leaders%20among%20SHG%20women%20members.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20also%20spoke%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20set%20a%20target%20to%20increase%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20police%20force%20to%2033%25%20of%20the%20total%20police%20strength%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%20survey%20and%20minorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20will%20also%20conduct%20a%20census%20or%20survey%20based%20on%20caste%20to%20accurately%20determine%20population%20and%20allocate%20benefits%20for%20informed%20decisions%20on%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20this%20exercise%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20government%20will%20undertake%20to%20provide%20reservations%20as%20per%20their%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%20also%20talks%20about%20the%20rights%20of%20these%20communities.%20If%20the%20party%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20it%20says%20it%20will%20establish%20an%20equal%20opportunities%20commission%20to%20ensure%20equal%20opportunities%20and%20fair%20representation%20for%20them.%20Adding%20to%20this%2C%20the%20party%20will%20modify%20the%20percentage%20of%20reservation%20for%20SC%2FST%20and%20OBC%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20actual%20population%20to%20be%20enumerated%20in%20the%20survey.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResearch%20centres%2C%20training%20facilities%2C%20and%20museums%20in%20Jaipur%20and%20Udaipur%20will%20be%20set%20up%20to%20nurture%20tribal%20youth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20party%20has%20promised%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20under%20the%20Mukhyamantri%20Nishulk%20Chiranjeevi%20Swasthya%20Bima%20Yojana.%20Recently%20the%20Congress%20Government%20in%20Rajasthan%20increased%20the%20medical%20cover%20under%20the%20Chiranjeevi%20Health%20Scheme%20from%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20annually%20per%20family.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20will%20also%20bring%20an%20education%20guarantee%20law%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20planned%20to%20uplift%20the%20underprivileged%20in%20rural%20areas%20by%20guaranteeing%20150%20days%20of%20employment%20annually%2C%20currently%20125%20days.%20Similar%20to%20the%20Kisan%20Credit%20Card%20Scheme%2C%20the%20government%20will%20implement%20a%20%E2%80%9CVyapari%20Credit%20Card%20Scheme%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20will%20withdraw%20pending%20cases%20against%20farmers%20related%20to%20their%20participation%20in%20protests%20and%20ensure%20their%20rights%20are%20safeguarded%2C%20it%20said.%20Farmers%20will%20get%20three-phase%20electricity%20support%20for%20eight%20hours%20a%20day%20from%20November%20to%20March%20each%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYouth%20will%20get%20more%20participation%20in%20leadership%20positions%20in%20government%20bodies.%20There%20will%20be%20a%20legislative%20fellowship%2C%20which%20will%20be%20similar%20to%20a%20parliamentary%20fellowship%2C%20giving%20youth%20leaders%20the%20opportunity%20to%20work%20with%20MLAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20ministers%20in%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700653707000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22171632%2FScreenshot-2023-11-22-at-5.16.13%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcaste-survey-minorities-farmers-women-in-focus-in-congress-manifesto%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Among%20other%20things%2C%20Congress%20also%20spoke%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20increase%20the%20representation%20of%20women%20in%20the%20police%20force%20to%2033%25%20of%20the%20police%20strength%20in%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcaste-survey-minorities-farmers-women-in-focus-in-congress-manifesto%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%E2%80%99ll%20Take%20Action%20Against%20Those%20Who%20Hide%20Behind%20Freedom%20of%20Speech%20to%20Provoke%20People%3A%20New%20J%26amp%3BK%20DGP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22165405%2Fimage-1527.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Seeking%20to%20draw%20a%20link%20between%20unknown%20%E2%80%98writers%E2%80%99%20and%20militancy%20recruitment%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20(DGP)%2C%20R.R.%20Swain%2C%20has%2C%20without%20specifying%20any%20examples%2C%20warned%20that%20any%20such%20%E2%80%98writing%E2%80%99%20will%20be%20treated%20as%20an%20%E2%80%98act%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20in%20Srinagar%20on%20Saturday%2C%20November%2018%2C%20Swain%20said%20that%20the%20recruitment%20of%20Kashmiri%20youngsters%20by%20militant%20groups%20shall%20be%20%E2%80%9Ctreated%20as%20an%20act%20of%20terror%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20people%20who%20purportedly%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20or%20facilitate%E2%80%9D%20militant%20recruitment%20%E2%80%9Care%20equally%20liable%20if%20not%20more%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20would%20be%20a%20sustained%20action%20against%20people%20who%20motivate%20and%20recruit%20(youngsters%20into%20militancy%20in%20J%26amp%3BK).%20Even%20people%20who%20write%20very%20differently%2C%20they%20are%20also%20liable%20for%20encouraging%20recruitment%2C%E2%80%9D%20DGP%20Swain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20take%20action%20against%20those%20who%20hide%20behind%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20to%20provoke%20people.%20We%20will%20not%20tolerate%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20appointed%20DGP%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20struck%20down%20the%20charges%20against%20journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%20under%20Sections%2018%20(terror%20conspiracy)%20and%20121%20(waging%20war%20against%20the%20country)%20of%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act%2C%201967%20(UAPA).%20The%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fafter-nearly-2-years-jk-hc-grants-bail-to-kashmir-walla-editor-fahad-shah%5C%22%3Egranted%20him%20bail%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20anti-terror%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Investigation%20Agency%20(SIA)%20had%20filed%20the%20case%20under%20various%20Sections%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20Foreign%20Contributions%20Regulation%20Act%20(FCRA)%2C%20after%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Findias-honour-not-its-incorporeal-property-says-jk-and-ladakh-hc-in-fahad-shah-order%2F%5C%22%3Eclaimed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20have%20received%20%E2%80%9Csource%20information%E2%80%9D%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EKashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Srinagar-based%20news%20outlet%20run%20by%20Shah%2C%20had%20published%20an%20article%20which%20was%20part%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Congoing%20operation%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cbreak%20up%20the%20Indian%20Union%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Csecession%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20from%20India%20and%20its%20consequent%20accession%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%20and%20Aala%20Fazili%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Kashmir%20scholar%20who%20had%20authored%20the%20piece%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20shackles%20of%20slavery%20will%20break%E2%80%99%2C%20were%20booked%20and%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%E2%80%99s%20elite%20counter-terrorism%20wing%2C%20DGP%20Swain%20was%20leading%20the%20SIA%20when%20the%20case%20was%20filed%20on%20April%204%2C%202022%20(FIR%20No%3A%2001%2F2022)%20at%20the%20CIJ%20police%20station%20in%20Jammu%2C%20and%20Aala%20and%20Shah%20were%20booked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20charge-sheet%2C%20the%20elite%20agency%2C%20which%20has%20overarching%20powers%20to%20take%20over%20militancy%20cases%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20article%20was%20part%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cterror%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20hatched%20by%20Pakistan%20to%20%E2%80%9Cincite%20violence%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20had%20led%20to%20%E2%80%9Cdisturbance%20in%20public%20order%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAala%20and%20Shah%20were%20accused%20of%20breach%20of%20peace%2C%20terrorism%20and%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20counsel%20and%20senior%20advocate%20P.N.%20Raina%20rejected%20the%20charges%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20SIA%20had%20%E2%80%9Cmysteriously%E2%80%9D%20discovered%20the%20article%2011%20years%20after%20its%20publication%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20of%20violence%2C%20breach%20of%20peace%20or%20any%20terror%20attack%20after%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20article.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20bail%20application%2C%20a%20division%20bench%20of%20the%20high%20court%20observed%20that%20the%20article%20called%20for%20secession%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20from%20India%20and%20also%20accused%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20for%20committing%20genocide%20of%20Kashmiris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20evidence%20of%20material%20damage%20caused%20to%20life%20or%20property%20by%20the%20purported%20write-up%2C%20which%20the%20prosecution%20sought%20to%20define%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98terrorist%20act%E2%80%99%20under%20Section%2015%20(1)%20(a)%20(ii)%20of%20the%20UAPA%2C%20the%20bench%20didn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20that%20the%20controversial%20article%20was%20an%20%E2%80%9Cattack%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%9D%20and%20an%20%E2%80%9Cact%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20this%20argument%20is%20accepted%2C%20it%20would%20literally%20turn%20criminal%20law%20on%20its%20head.%20It%20would%20mean%20that%20any%20criticism%20of%20the%20central%20government%20can%20be%20described%20as%20a%20terrorist%20act%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Mohan%20Lal%20and%20Atul%20Sreedharan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20observed%20that%20none%20of%20the%20six%20prosecution%20witnesses%20examined%20so%20far%20in%20the%20trial%20have%20testified%20that%20there%20was%20any%20breach%20of%20peace%20or%20attack%20on%20security%20forces%20due%20to%20the%20publication%20of%20the%20article%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20court%20linked%20the%20write-up%20to%20the%20freedom%20of%20speech%20and%20expression%20while%20granting%20bail%20to%20Shah%2C%20who%20will%20now%20face%20trial%20under%20Section%2013%20(abetting%20unlawful%20activities)%20of%20the%20UAPA%20and%20FCRA%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20framed%20the%20charges%20against%20Aala%20and%20Shah%20in%20March%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShah%2C%20who%20has%20been%20booked%20in%20three%20other%20cases%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20was%20also%20taken%20into%20preventive%20detention%20under%20the%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20(PSA)%20earlier%20this%20year.%20However%2C%20the%20PSA%20proceedings%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffahad-shah-public-safety-act-jammu-kashmir-high-court%5C%22%3Ewere%20also%20quashed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SIA%2C%20which%20probed%20the%20case%20against%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Kashmir%20Walla%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20was%20formed%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20for%20%E2%80%9Cspeedy%20and%20effective%20investigation%20and%20prosecution%20of%20militancy-related%20cases%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Conference%20and%20Peoples%E2%80%99%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20among%20other%20regional%20parties%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fnew-anti-terrorism-body-state-investigation-agency-formed-in-jk%2Farticle37297553.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20expressed%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20SIA%E2%80%99s%20formation%2C%20saying%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Caimed%20to%20strengthen%20the%20repressive%20apparatus%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20administration%2C%20which%20is%20run%20by%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%2C%20had%20sought%20to%20allay%20the%20apprehensions%20by%20arguing%20that%20the%20agency%20was%20an%20important%20step%20to%20curb%20terrorism%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700653531000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22165405%2Fimage-1527.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwell-take-action-against-those-who-hide-behind-freedom-of-speech-to-provoke-people-new-jk-dgp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22DGP%20R.R.%20Swain%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20high%20court%20struck%20down%20the%20charges%20against%20journalist%20Fahad%20Shah%20under%20sections%20of%20the%20UAPA%2C%20while%20granting%20him%20bail%20in%20an%20anti-terror%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwell-take-action-against-those-who-hide-behind-freedom-of-speech-to-provoke-people-new-jk-dgp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22French%20pilot%20sentenced%20for%20decapitating%20skydiver%20with%20wing%20of%20plane%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700653019000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3DA2%2Fproduction%2F_131787751_gettyimages-1336524201.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67494130%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nicolas%20Galy%2C%2040%2C%20died%20after%20being%20struck%20by%20the%20aircraft%20he%20had%20jumped%20out%20of%20seconds%20before.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A409%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67494130%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67494130.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67494130.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20we%20know%20about%20Israel-Ham