the%20chief%20minister%20has%20worked%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%3F%20Don%E2%80%99t%20you%20see%20his%20schemes%3F%E2%80%9D%20This%20statement%20comes%20as%20a%20strong%20endorsement%20of%20the%20incumbent%20chief%20minister%20Ashok%20Gehlot%2C%20under%20whose%20government%20Dhariwal%20serves%20as%20the%20urban%20development%20and%20housing%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20later%2C%20Dhariwal%20added%20that%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20senior%20leadership%20will%20decide%20who%20the%20next%20chief%20minister%20will%20be%20and%20that%20he%20will%20abide%20by%20the%20senior%20leadership%E2%80%99s%20decision.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7jmpQjiIe3k%3Fsi%3DaC_G9_SKGbsdnmdW%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDhariwal%E2%80%99s%20constituency%2C%20Kota%20(North)%2C%20known%20as%20a%20second%20home%20for%20thousands%20of%20students%20preparing%20for%20NEET-JEE%20exams%2C%20has%20unfortunately%20witnessed%20a%20surge%20in%20suicides%20this%20year.%20On%20this%20matter%2C%20Dhariwal%20chose%20not%20to%20delve%20into%20specifics%20and%20simply%20called%20it%20an%20%E2%80%9Cold%20matter%E2%80%9D%20that%20he%20did%20not%20wish%20to%20address.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Dhariwal%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20projects%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Rs%2014%2C000%20crore%20Chambal%20riverfront%20development%20%E2%80%93%20ran%20into%20controversy%20this%20year.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20opposition%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20riverfront%20construction%20has%20adversely%20affected%20wildlife.%20Former%20MLA%20Prahlad%20Gunjal%20from%20Kota%20(North)%20contended%20that%20the%20area%2C%20where%20the%20riverfront%20is%20located%2C%20is%20a%20crocodile%20sanctuary%20with%20a%20designated%20eco-sensitive%20zone%20extending%20up%20to%2010%20kilometres.%20The%20matter%20is%20set%20to%20be%20investigated%20by%20the%20National%20Green%20Tribunal%20(NGT)%2C%20and%20Dhariwal%20asserted%20his%20openness%20to%20scrutiny%2C%20emphasising%20that%20all%20necessary%20steps%20were%20taken%20before%20initiating%20the%20project.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20questions%20about%20the%20delay%20in%20finalising%20his%20ticket%20and%20rumours%20of%20corruption%2C%20Dhariwal%20clarified%20that%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%2C%20many%20people%20complained%20against%20him%20to%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20This%20prompted%20an%20investigation%20by%20a%20team%20set%20up%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20Dhariwal%20was%20subsequently%20cleared%20of%20any%20corruption%20allegations%20and%20granted%20the%20party%20ticket.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDhariwal%E2%80%99s%20name%20has%20become%20a%20catchphrase%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20political%20discourse%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20assembly%20elections%20because%20of%20a%20controversial%20statement%20he%20made%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20where%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ERajasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Emardon%3C%2Fem%3E%20ka%20pradesh%20hai%20(It%E2%80%99s%20a%20man%E2%80%99s%20land).%E2%80%9D%20In%20his%20defence%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20did%20say%20that%2C%20but%20why%20is%20the%20opposition%20only%20questioning%20that%20part%3F%20Why%20are%20they%20not%20showing%20the%20complete%20video%20where%20I%20also%20criticised%20this%20serious%20issue%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Rajasthan%20gears%20up%20for%20elections%20on%20November%2025%2C%20these%20developments%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20a%20dynamic%20political%20landscape%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700649903000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewir