22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajasthan-will-mp-rajyavardhan-rathod-seal-the-deal-in-jhotwara%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tracing%20the%20Long%2C%20Complex%20History%20of%20Debate%20on%20Caste%20Census%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20has%20caused%20quite%20a%20clamour.%20Counterintuitively%2C%20the%20survey%20has%20revealed%20that%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20and%20Extremely%20Backward%20Classes%20(EBCs)%20together%20make%20up%20over%2063%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%20Indeed%2C%20since%20its%20revelation%2C%20livid%20ultimatums%20by%20the%20opposition%20have%20demanded%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20exercise%20in%20other%20states.%20This%20curious%20insistence%20might%20make%20it%20seem%20that%20the%20opposition%2C%20which%20has%20bandwagoned%20for%20the%20census%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%E2%80%98social%20justice%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20always%20been%20in%20favour%20of%20enumerating%20caste.%20However%2C%20a%20longer%20history%20of%20the%20politics%20around%20the%20caste%20census%20reveals%20mixed%20attitudes%20on%20the%20statistical%20enumeration%20of%20caste%20by%20prominent%20political%20parties%2C%20even%20those%20that%20vociferously%20demand%20it%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20on%20the%20first%20post-Independence%20census%20included%20discussions%20on%20whether%20to%20include%20caste%20as%20a%20parameter.%20Ambedkar%20was%20crisp%20on%20why%20an%20up-to-date%20database%20was%20instrumental%20in%20formulating%20policy%20measures%20and%20ensuring%20representation%20of%20the%20diverse%20communities%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20championed%20the%20idea%20of%20collecting%20caste-based%20data%20for%20purposes%20of%20affirmative%20action%20in%20the%20first%20post-Independence%20census%20of%201951.%20However%2C%20this%20would%20imply%20that%20caste%20enumeration%20would%20be%20limited%20to%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs).%20Following%20this%20logic%2C%20the%20state%20under%20Nehruvian%20leadership%20made%20a%20policy%20decision%20not%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste-wise%20population%20enumeration%2C%20except%20for%20the%20scheduled%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fneed-of-the-hour-a-selfie-called-caste-census-india-must-confront-its-truth%5C%22%3ENeed%20of%20the%20Hour%3A%20A%20Selfie%20Called%20Caste%20Census%20%E2%80%93%20India%20Must%20Confront%20its%20Truth%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollation%20of%20caste-based%20data%2C%20other%20than%20for%20purposes%20of%20affirmative%20action%2C%20was%20seen%20as%20ironically%20%E2%80%98entrenching%20the%20caste%20system%E2%80%99.%20Unironically%2C%20following%20Independence%2C%20the%201951%20census%20data%20on%20caste%20was%20never%20made%20public.%20Concerns%20of%20privacy%2C%20potential%20misuse%2C%20social%20unrest%2C%20and%20even%20state%20capacity%20to%20assemble%20such%20data%20with%20accuracy%20were%20cited%20as%20reasons.%20In%20the%20thick%20of%20many%20of%20these%20concerns%20and%20the%20administrative%20challenges%20of%20processing%20such%20voluminous%20and%20potentially%20controversial%20data%2C%20subsequent%20debates%20on%20caste%20enumeration%20were%20delayed%2C%20if%20not%20completely%20evaded.%20Again%2C%20the%20grand%20narrative%20of%20%E2%80%98national%20integration%E2%80%99%20was%20instrumentalised%20%E2%80%93%20Indians%20had%20to%20%E2%80%98move%20beyond%20caste%E2%80%99%20once%20and%20for%20all.%20In%20the%20nearly%2030%20years%20of%20uninterrupted%20Congress%20rule%20since%20Independence%2C%20caste%20and%20its%20enumeration%20became%20feeble%20cries%20in%20parliamentary%20debates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPost-Mandal%20scenario%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20wrangles%20around%20caste%20and%20the%20politics%20of%20recognition%20resurfaced%20in%20the%201970s%2C%2080s%2C%20and%2090s%20with%20the%20Mandal%20Commission.%20The%20commission%20recommended%20expanding%20reservation%20for%20government%20jobs%20to%20include%20%E2%80%98backward%20classes%E2%80%99%2C%20based%20on%20the%201931%20census%20data%20collated%20by%20the%20colonial%20government.%20In%20his%20early%20political%20career%20in%20the%201970s%2C%20much%20before%20he%20left%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20V.P.%20Singh%20had%20marked%20his%20support%20for%20the%20Commission%20and%20his%20advocacy%20for%20caste-based%20affirmative%20action.%20Such%20discussions%20were%20closely%20related%20to%20discussions%20about%20the%20collection%20of%20caste%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F24155349%2FMandal-Commission.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F24155349%2FMandal-Commission.jpg%20650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2F24155349%2FMandal-Commission-300x210.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-282852%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22455%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EFile%20photo.%20B.P.%20Mandal%20submitting%20copies%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20report%20to%20Gyani%20Zail%20Singh%2C%20former%20President%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20movement%2C%20Kanshiram%20in%20his%20batty%20retorts%20personified%20that%20the%20census%20as%20a%20much-needed%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20surgery%E2%80%9D%20whereby%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbackward%20classes%20would%20be%20given%20their%20due%20share%E2%80%9D.%20%C2%A0After%20much%20delay%2C%20finally%2C%20in%201990%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Mandal%20Commission%20resulted%20in%20the%20introduction%20of%20OBC%20reservations.%20The%20Mandal%20Commission%20estimated%20the%20OBC%20population%20at%2052%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20staunchly%20opposed%20to%20the%20Commission%20and%20its%20recommendations.%20Advani%2C%20who%20at%20this%20time%20went%20about%20rabble-rousing%20the%20masses%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98rath%20yatra%E2%80%99%20that%20culminated%20in%20the%20demolition%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20patronisingly%20caricatured%20the%20recommendations%20as%20%E2%80%9Cwell-intentioned%E2%80%9D%20but%20emphasised%20that%20reservations%20were%20%E2%80%9Cdiluting%20the%20emphasis%20on%20merit-based%20selection%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvp-singh-mandal-commission%5C%22%3E30%20Years%20On%2C%20Mandal%20Commission%20Is%20Still%20a%20Mirror%20for%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%2C%20even%20as%20its%20broad%20rhetoric%20scrawled%20in%20favour%20of%20caste%20enumeration%20for%20affirmative%20action%2C%20there%20were%20elusive%20opinions%20afloat%20on%20a%20complete%20caste%20census.%20Post-Mandal%2C%20the%20party%20faced%20a%20complex%20political%20landscape%20and%20its%20stance%20became%20entangled%20with%20electoral%20considerations.%20Considerations%20of%20potential%20electoral%20implications%20implied%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20had%20to%20%E2%80%98balance%E2%80%99%20the%20interests%20of%20various%20social%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20history%2C%20the%20recent%20fervour%20surrounding%20the%20Bihar%20caste%20census%20serves%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20ongoing%20struggle%20between%20electoral%20concerns%20and%20actual%20attempts%20by%20the%20state%20to%20ameliorate%20social%20inequities.%20Indeed%2C%20in%20a%20country%20where%20caste-based%20voting%20blocs%20play%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20electoral%20outcomes%2C%20a%20caste%20census%20could%20open%20a%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20box.%20After%20all%2C%20enumeration%20is%20also%20a%20process%20of%20creation%2C%20standardisation%20and%20reification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStance%20of%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20within%20the%20present-day%20state%20that%20has%20sought%20to%20broaden%20its%20reach%20and%20increase%20the%20legibility%20of%20its%20population%2C%20the%20omission%20of%20caste%20as%20a%20categorisation%20is%20puzzling.%20Citizens%20today%20are%20required%20to%20possess%20a%20never-ending%20list%20of%20documents%20to%20%E2%80%98prove%E2%80%99%20their%20identity%20to%20the%20state%3A%20Aadhaars%2C%20ration%20cards%2C%20passports%2C%20civil%20registers%2C%20and%20various%20types%20of%20censuses.%20Yet%2C%20despite%20this%20increased%20enumerative%20logic%2C%20caste%20%E2%80%93%20which%20remains%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20a%20primary%20logic%20of%20identity%20construction%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20has%20remained%20as%20elusive%20as%20ever.%20The%20absence%20of%20data%20makes%20it%20impossible%20to%20account%20for%20the%20ever-worsening%20social%20inequities%20in%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvasion%20around%20discussions%20of%20enumerating%20caste%2C%20citing%20uneven%20state%20capacity%2C%20was%20possible%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20Independence.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20case%20anymore.%20With%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20many%20ways%20the%20state%20has%20attempted%20to%20expand%20every%20other%20form%20of%20enumeration%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20incentives%20to%20omit%20caste%20as%20an%20enumerative%20category%20are%20deeply%20political%20and%20motivated%20by%20electoral%20calculus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20adhering%20to%20constitutional%20mandate%20(Article%20340)%2C%20statistical%20enumeration%20has%20become%20all%20the%20more%20important%20today.%20Even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F102852%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EM.%20Nagaraj%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%2C%202006%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20case%20has%20demanded%20that%20%E2%80%9Cquantifiable%20data%E2%80%9D%20was%20a%20requisite%20%E2%80%9Cto%20demonstrate%20backwardness%20and%20inadequate%20representation%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20government%20initiated%20the%20Socio-economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20(2011)%2C%20showing%20how%20there%20is%20a%20greater%20willingness%2C%20at%20least%20from%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Congress%20to%20collect%20caste-related%20data%20for%20policy%20planning%20and%20resource%20allocation.%20The%20ruling%20regime%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20around%20the%20Census%20shows%20that%20enumeration%20will%20not%20only%20fundamentally%20restructure%20welfare%20politics%20and%20affirmative%20action%20but%20will%20also%20potentially%20shift%20the%20electoral%20base%20of%20political%20parties.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20prominent%20parties%20having%20no%20fixed%20position%20on%20the%20census%20have%20begun%20to%20engineer%20their%20politics%20to%20finesse%20shifting%20demographics%20and%20electoral%20tides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENoel%20Mariam%20George%20is%20a%20research%20scholar%20in%20International%20History%20at%20the%20London%20School%20of%20Economics.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700647245000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftracing-the-long-complex-history-of-debate-on-caste-census%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20political%20parties%20that%20vociferously%20demand%20caste%20census%20today%20had%20mixed%20opinions%20about%20it%20at%20one%20point.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20more%20or%20less%20remained%20opposed%20to%20the%20idea%20due%20to%20its%20ideological%20and%20electoral%20considerations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Ftracing-the-long-complex-history-of-debate-on-caste-census%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Support%20Journalists%20While%20They%E2%80%99re%20Alive%E2%80%99%3A%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20Arfa%20Khanum%20Sherwani%26nbsp%3BAwarded%20Chhatrapati%20Samman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F22144417%2Fimage-1525.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Arfa%20Khanum%20Sherwani%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20senior%20editor%2C%20received%20the%20Chhatrapati%20Samman%20award%20on%20November%2022%2C%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhanum%20Sherwani%20dedicated%20her%20award%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20journalists%20killed%20in%20the%20line%20of%20duty%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20journalists%20to%20get%20killed%2C%20support%20them%20while%20they%20are%20alive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20her%20acceptance%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20journalism%20is%20going%20through%20its%20worst%20phase%20in%20history.%20We%20are%20living%20in%20a%20time%20where%20journalists%20are%20being%20branded%20as%20terrorists%20and%20enemies%20of%20the%20nation.%20While%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20mainstream%20media%20has%20become%20an%20extension%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20propaganda%20machinery%2C%20those%20of%20us%20who%20are%20still%20questioning%20the%20most%20powerful%20people%20and%20raising%20issues%20of%20the%20marginalised%20%5Bcommunities%5D%20are%20being%20punished%20in%20the%20worst%20possible%20ways.%20The%20people%20in%20power%20are%20dehumanising%20journalists%20to%20a%20point%20where%20any%20action%20against%20them%20can%20be%20justified.%20They%20are%20being%20hounded%20and%20prosecuted%20under%20anti-terror%20laws%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20in%20the%20last%20one%20decade%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20alternate%20media%2C%20a%20byproduct%20of%20the%20demise%20of%20legacy%20media%2C%20is%20good%20news%20for%20democracy.%20Despite%20limited%20resources%2C%20and%20against%20all%20odds%2C%20platforms%20like%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20doing%20the%20crucial%20job%20of%20informing%20and%20educating%20people%20about%20their%20rights%20and%20creating%20a%20more%20informed%20citizenry.%20Mass%20movements%20like%20the%20Shaheen%20Bagh%20movement%20and%20Kisan%20Andolan%20are%20proof%20that%20the%20battle%20of%20truth%20and%20democracy%20will%20be%20fought%2C%20and%20one%20day%20won%20by%20our%20poorest%20and%20most%20marginalised%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20people%20in%20power%20and%20their%20supporters%20online%20and%20offline%20attack%20me%20and%20use%20my%20religious%20identity%20to%20discredit%20my%20work%20as%20a%20journalist.%20Despite%20rape%20and%20death%20threats%2C%20I%20remain%20undettered%20because%20my%20greatest%20support%20comes%20from%20ordinary%20viewers%20like%20you.%20But%20like%20Ram%20Chander%20Chhatrapati%2C%20people%20should%20not%20wait%20for%20a%20journalist%20to%20get%20killed%2C%20support%20them%20while%20they%20are%20alive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERam%20Chander%20Chhatrapati%2C%20who%20was%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EPoora%20Sach%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20published%20from%20Sirsa%20in%20Haryana%2C%20was%20killed%20on%20October%2024%2C%202002.%20For%20him%2C%20journalism%20was%20a%20mission%20to%20take%20on%20the%20high%20and%20the%20mighty%20who%20misused%20their%20position%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20the%20common%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChhatrapati%20had%20found%20incriminating%20evidence%20against%20Dera%20Sacha%20Sauda%20chief%2C%20Gurmeet%20Ram%20Rahim%20S