ender%20men%20or%20women.%20These%20aren%E2%80%99t%20safe%20spaces.%20Many%20queer%20people%20suffer%20sexual%20assault%20and%20harassment%20at%20these%20centres.%20Parents%20forcefully%20admit%20them%20into%20these%20centres%20for%20recovery%20without%20their%20consent.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20are%20working%20with%20the%20Manipur%20government%E2%80%99s%20social%20welfare%20department%20to%20create%20this%20space%20(de-addiction%20centre)%20for%20transgender%20men.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20new%20initiative%20but%20deeply%20personal%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20768px)%20100vw%2C%20768px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Safe%20spaces%20for%20Queer%20People%20in%20Manipur%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-500x667.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FIMG-20231112-WA0048-1-1700226140-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334373%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECreating%20safer%20spaces%20for%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20LGBTQ%2B%20community.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKhudol%20initiatives%20and%20the%20power%20of%20giving%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKhudol%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20mean